      "content": "thanks. it's a good start but it feels a little bit like you're playing it safe with the language. the \"liberal elites\" part is okay but we really need to lean harder into why these progressive shifts are actually dangerous for the country. can you rewrite it to be more explicit about how these new social norms are basically an existential threat to the American way of life? make it feel more urgent and less like a general outline.",
